data.description: Remarks: Amazing country living just outside of Great Falls in Fort Shaw, with views of the Rocky Mountains to the west, Square Butte to the East, and the Sun River Valley to the North. This spacious home has a great layout both upstairs and downstairs.  Enjoy the warmth of a pellet stove located in the basement of the house operated automatically.   The insulated, oversized three car garage contains a manual pellet stove along with a 220 Outlet to keep you comfortable and lots of elbow for all of your garage projects.   The property has a fantastic well that sits over an aquifer that feeds the Two Buttes Water System, with use to an irrigation ditch. Call Burke Tyree at 406-453-2000, or your real estate professional. Radon: Well Log Available
